data.description: Welcome to the desirable swim/tennis community of Bradford Place, where you'll find this classic 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home that's sure to delight. The floor plan is designed to accommodate both family life and entertaining. This home has received several upgrades, including new siding, LVP (Luxury Vinyl Plank) flooring, fresh paint, a newer roof, and HVAC, among other improvements. Outside, the private, fenced backyard is a haven for kids and pets to play freely and securely. Conveniently located close to shopping, restaurants, and schools, this home offers a wonderful combination of comfort, style, and accessibility. It's an excellent find that's ready to welcome its new owners.
